{"tid":777712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Mina谷胸影婚照 甜蜜放閃曬恩愛","createTime":"2018-08-13T06:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T11:47:16.000Z","uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c11529da71733fbb3bee063be1061d8f7ca340","tid":777712,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"韓國45歲女歌手Mina與年輕17歲的韓星Phillip於2015年8月公開「母子戀」，今年3月註冊結婚，並於7月在首爾江南區的Wedding Hall舉行婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n新娘子Mina日前在Instagram發表感想：「我們『菲美夫婦』終於在今天結婚了，可以在那麼多人的祝福下舉行婚禮，真的既光榮又感謝，雖然為了要打破社會的偏見而經歷過艱難的時期，但我們憑着長時間的相處和對彼此的信任，愛情終於結果，我們也會幸福和美麗地生活的，大家也要幸福啊，謝謝。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/142610_8884627e504d89118a1e800430b1b6d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F142610_8884627e504d89118a1e800430b1b6d8.jpg&h=8a780926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n45歲女歌手Mina與年輕17歲的韓星Phillip終收成正果，結為夫妻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/142650_f3073b07eeb9ea778efc360f4ba853ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F142650_f3073b07eeb9ea778efc360f4ba853ea.jpg&h=67556fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMina公開結婚照大晒幸福。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/142855_9ef3c2cdd81e0e781cb09878d39413a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F142855_9ef3c2cdd81e0e781cb09878d39413a2.jpg&h=69f090fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMina與Phillip喺關島嘅渡蜜月。"},{"pid":"1ea73f922dc4820bd1362369014938ae541925bf","tid":777712,"uid":130950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"重膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927a60dac4414463712fc8cc80689e647e55028d","tid":777712,"uid":1880,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"